room_title: Escape room "The Hunted" by Escape Mission Chattanooga in Chattanooga
review: We went on our first escape for my boyfriend's birthday! Our mission was The Hunted. We ended up with only 4 people in our group but we were able to pull it off and we escaped! We can't wait to go back!

room_title: Escape room "The Hunted" by Escape Mission Chattanooga in Chattanooga
review: We have been to multiple different escape rooms at different places, and Escape Mission Chattanooga was definitely one of our best experiences! We chose The Hunted and this room was such a great challenge! The staff was also very friendly, and very easy to work with! We will definitely be back!
